data.description: Been searching for your own Private Sanctuary?  Tranquility and Peace surround you here on this manicured 2.43 Ac lot. 1993 Skyline , 1512 SF., 3bd,2ba,Spacious floorplan. Kitchen has nook with desk area, wrap around counter with a open "window bar" to living room for conversation and delivery of beverages and food! LARGE-Master bedroom with walk-in closet with ample room. Bay window in corner leading to oversized bathroom with duel sinks, separate vanity area, mirrored tub, linen closet and separate shower! Additional 8x14 insulated mud room off utility room with elect and insulated door holds extra refer and freezer,(not included in SF) Off dining room which has built in china cabinet,  sliding doors lead you to a full deck 10 x 34 is covered to enjoy seasonally, and additional 12x15 is open air to enjoy lovely evenings and watch the herds of Elk pass bay, rest and sun bathe!! THEN there is a 24 x 36 shop/garage with garage door opener, 220 & 110 elect for work area, work bench and storage, plenty of room for vehicles, concrete floor.  RV Carport with water, elect, and concrete slab is next to shop. A gardeners  dream yard here! Wrapped & framed in green heavy duty netting, blueberry field and raspberries climb up side of wood shed, plus garden! Treed with Willow, Fir ,Maples, Birch, etc., assorted fruit trees (Elk love them) and shrubs. 4 water spikets located on property, 1 for RV, 1 garden area, 2 out in large yard. The 2 spikets are capped off for winter. One at top of pipe, and one about 12 inches under ground, due to break in pipe. Seller had capped off below ground level, but can reactivate it in current location or move??  Wood/Tool 12x17 shop with elect and concrete floor also. Pump house has had recent repairs. Great tasting water.  In Reality...you just have to EXPERIENCE this lovely property. PRIDE OF OWNERSHIP - ONE OWNER FOR 30 years!! Started with bare-raw land!! Aprox 8mi/f beach APT ONLY ***PLEASE ONLY PRE-APPROVED**
